  "intent_precise": "qPCR Prep with 384 Well Plate: Using deepwell_pro (deep_well_plate, slot 1), pcr_plate (pcr_plate, slot 2), primer_pairs (deep_well_plate, slot 3), temp_plate (labware, slot 5). With temperature module. (1) Set temperature to temp\u00b0C. (2) Transfer 30\u00b5L from source to destination. (3) Mix 4 times at 40\u00b5L. (4) Transfer 10\u00b5L from source to destination. (5) Transfer 5\u00b5L from source to destination.",
